channel.title: "The American toddler who got car keys lodged in his brain..." And was unharmed?
channel.description:
Sup guys. I heard about this after watching a video on it, from a YouTuber (FLuffee Talks). Although it's old, it's pretty amazing. Honestly, it's pretty hard to say why he was unharmed. I wanted to hear your opinions on it.
News link: http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1089309/Pictured-The-American-toddler-got-set-car-keys-lodged-brain---recovered-unscathed.html
Again, I didn't find this myself.
~Lin
